CLASS zcl_rap_book_handler DEFINITION PUBLIC FINAL CREATE PUBLIC.
  PUBLIC SECTION. INTERFACES if_abap_rap_handler.
  METHODS: before_read FOR MODIFY IMPORTING keys FOR READ Books,
